1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 21=

11
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,479
Big talk.

12
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,159
You're asking for it.

13
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,680
Yingying!

14
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,159
You go first.

15
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:09,959
Wubing...

16
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,000
Su Wubing.

17
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,000
Ningxue.

18
00:01:33,439 --> 00:01:34,239
Ningxue.

19
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,000
What is this?

20
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,480
Ningxue!

21
00:01:59,079 --> 00:01:59,879
Ningxue!

22
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:01,560
Don't go!

23
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,360
That was

24
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,639
Ningxue's divine sense.

25
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,080
She's still trapped in the illusion.

26
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,080
Finally caught on?

27
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:20,840
You aren't that impressive, huh?

28
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:25,439
Her divine sense has been stuck
in ancient times.

29
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:29,759
You'll never break her curse.

30
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,680
Su Wubing,

31
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:33,599
you really think you can

32
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:35,439
change everything by yourself?

33
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,479
Now get down

34
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,800
on your knees for m-my Senior.

35
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,960
If he's pleased,

36
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,360
maybe you'll get a quick death.

37
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,360
You want to save her? No chance.

38
00:02:56,280 --> 00:03:00,400
This ancient demonic power
was meant for you.

39
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,560
Even every god in heaven

40
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:05,840
couldn't last a minute in it.

41
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,599
Your soul is mine!

42
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,080
Sword, come!

43
00:03:39,639 --> 00:03:41,159
You have reforged the sword?

44
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:45,199
Have you regained
the Immortal King's Heavenly God Realm?

45
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,400
Immortal King?

46
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:50,080
He really is the Immortal King.

47
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:51,680
Senior.

48
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,639
He can't be the Immortal King.

49
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:55,719
Otherwise, he wouldn't
need these mortals to save him.

50
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,759
Senior.

51
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,159
You promised me

52
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:03,080
you'd take his life.

53
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,240
Impossible.

54
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:11,479
Su Wubing is nothing to fear.

55
00:04:11,599 --> 00:04:12,639
Just finish him!

56
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:16,279
A mere ant dares to make noise?

57
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:20,399
S-Senior, what are you doing?

58
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:23,439
Your job is done.

59
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,199
No use keeping you around.

60
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,959
Might as well use you
to boost my cultivation.

61
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:30,839
Consider it your contribution
to the Demon Clan.

62
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:37,759
Since you've reached
the Heavenly God Realm,

63
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:40,360
I'd be interested
to cross swords with you.

64
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,800
Since you insist,

65
00:04:44,279 --> 00:04:46,680
I'll grant your wish.

66
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,600
Grant my wish?

67
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:55,040
They say an Immortal King's sword
can split the spirit mountains.

68
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:58,160
One strike can unleash
fifty years of power.

69
00:04:58,519 --> 00:05:02,920
But you've spent a thousand years
as a mere mortal.

70
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,040
Even if you've awakened divine power,

71
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:08,279
you're not what you used to be.

72
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:11,480
You can't strike the way you once did.

73
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,079
Pity indeed.

74
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,199
You won't live to see that strike.

75
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:18,079
In that case,

76
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,399
I'll kill Lin Ningxue first.

77
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,839
Once you have a weakness,

78
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,480
you have an opening.

79
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:31,399
As long as

80
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:33,000
you can't let go your obsession,

81
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,000
no matter how many times you're reborn,

82
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,399
you're still nothing but an ant.

83
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,480
Let go now, and it's not too late.

84
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,319
Let go?

85
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:49,040
The Ancient God Sect
has waited all this time

86
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,560
for this very moment.

87
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,360
How is this possible?

88
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,160
This strike...

89
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,879
may not carry sixty years of power,

90
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,879
but it's more than enough to kill you.

91
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:18,759
Even if I die,

92
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:22,240
I'll drag Lin Ningxue down with me.

93
00:06:49,405 --> 00:06:53,508
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

94
00:06:53,508 --> 00:06:58,228
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

95
00:06:58,228 --> 00:07:03,108
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

96
00:07:03,108 --> 00:07:08,228
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

97
00:07:08,228 --> 00:07:12,628
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

98
00:07:12,628 --> 00:07:17,308
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

99
00:07:17,308 --> 00:07:22,708
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

100
00:07:22,708 --> 00:07:29,102
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

